name: Mona - Genshin Impact (Character)
description:
Version 2!

This is a LORA of the character Mona Megistus from Hoyoverse's Genshin Impact. This was trained on Anything4.5 with Clip Skip 2.

To prompt the full character, enter "<lora:MonaGenshinImpactv2:strength>GIMona, megistus hat, bodystocking, choker, hair ribbon, capelet, hair ornament, earring, high heels," To remove parts of the outfit, such as the hat, simply do not prompt that article of clothing, and/or put it into the negative prompt.

This new version of this LORA is trained at higher resolution with a larger dataset, increases general detail fidelity, corrects her hair color, style, and face details.

modelVersions.name: v2
